WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:01.760
Good morning, family.

00:00:01.760 --> 00:00:03.199
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.199 --> 00:00:07.702
I believe this is day 10, if I'm not mistaken.

00:00:10.960 --> 00:00:12.200
We're in the double digits.

00:00:12.200 --> 00:00:16.175
Maybe it's day 11; I'll have to ask my son.

00:00:16.175 --> 00:00:22.160
It all goes together for me, but I had some things on my heart.

00:00:26.040 --> 00:00:28.400
The Lord wants me to bring it up again.

00:00:31.058 --> 00:00:32.800
Jesus is the Healer.

00:00:35.920 --> 00:00:42.480
I've been thinking about it because of the meetings I've been in the last three days.

00:00:42.960 --> 00:00:44.347
People are getting healed.

00:00:44.347 --> 00:01:31.486
I'm seeing people walk away believing for their manifestation, while some get theirs instantaneously.

00:01:32.103 --> 00:02:05.059
You see the bondage of Satan's work falling off.

00:02:14.807 --> 00:03:11.680
I know beyond a shadow of a doubt we are about to see great manifestations of the glory of God beyond anybody's comprehension.

00:03:11.680 --> 00:03:42.730
We are in the last seconds of the last days.

00:03:42.730 --> 00:04:06.587
I'm going to keep saying it: Jesus Christ is coming.

00:04:06.587 --> 00:04:52.460
There's a work to be done; the harvest is plentiful, but the laborers are few.

00:04:53.380 --> 00:05:37.957
I pray you are being a light in the darkness—at your workplace, the store, or school.

00:05:37.957 --> 00:06:09.680
Be a light shining bright for the world to see.

00:06:27.213 --> 00:07:00.447
There was a night I was praying and one of my friends called.

00:07:08.920 --> 00:07:18.800
They were overcoming severe arthritis.

00:07:18.800 --> 00:07:48.100
He asked me, 'Brandon, why aren't all Christians healed?

00:07:48.100 --> 00:08:46.232
' I told him I don't have all the answers, but I'll ask the Lord.

00:08:46.232 --> 00:09:28.469
It bothered me because some people I pray for get healed and some don't.

00:09:28.469 --> 00:09:42.880
You can get weary in well-doing.

00:09:52.302 --> 00:10:58.759
I heard a message from a preacher who said to always stay on God's side, even if you don't understand what you're walking through.

00:11:13.090 --> 00:11:19.970
Never get angry at God.

00:11:23.466 --> 00:12:06.226
Like Job, who stood his ground: 'Though He slay me, yet will I praise Him.

00:12:06.226 --> 00:12:47.862
' No matter the circumstance, God is a good God.

00:12:47.862 --> 00:13:47.260
People in the body of Christ, even in the Word of Faith movement, often don't answer the hard questions.

00:13:47.260 --> 00:14:03.600
Brother Hagin always did.

00:14:03.600 --> 00:15:05.097
That's why I go through the old archives from Brother Hagin and feast as much as I can.

00:15:05.097 --> 00:15:54.000
He was a diamond in the rough of all the ministers I've listened to.

00:15:54.000 --> 00:16:22.150
Brother Hagin changed my life; he had a teaching anointing.

00:16:23.688 --> 00:17:01.829
I wish he were still here, but his season was over.

00:17:17.719 --> 00:17:43.640
I went to sleep that night and had an experience with the Lord.

00:17:43.640 --> 00:18:08.719
In this experience, I was at Jesus' crucifixion.

00:18:08.719 --> 00:18:36.831
He was a young man, 33 years old.

00:18:51.306 --> 00:19:01.519
I saw him right before he was scourged.

00:19:01.519 --> 00:19:44.711
I was standing there with the Father and Jesus, watching Jesus in the past being whipped.

00:19:47.679 --> 00:20:01.720
It felt like real time.

00:20:06.533 --> 00:20:27.223
I could smell the livestock and the animal feces.

00:20:28.869 --> 00:21:07.016
The sun was shining and it felt about 85 degrees.

00:21:07.016 --> 00:21:37.787
His skin was sweating and dirty; he was olive-complected.

00:21:37.787 --> 00:22:10.916
His hands were strapped by metal bands to a whipping post.

00:22:10.916 --> 00:22:27.680
There were two soldiers.

00:22:27.680 --> 00:23:04.940
One was a very large man, bald, and massively built.

00:23:04.940 --> 00:23:51.460
The other was a Roman guard with a breastplate and a kilt-looking outfit.

00:23:51.460 --> 00:24:20.193
They were cracking those whips to intimidate him.

00:24:32.223 --> 00:24:47.010
I saw them whip him, and blood splattered everywhere.

00:24:47.010 --> 00:25:16.880
Chunks of flesh were pulled from his body.

00:25:19.099 --> 00:25:25.804
I screamed, 'Stop it!

00:25:25.804 --> 00:25:43.213
' I saw them ripping his beard out.

00:25:43.213 --> 00:26:13.759
They tortured him as they tore him to pieces.

00:26:13.759 --> 00:26:51.440
When they were done, he dangled there as a bloody mess.

00:26:51.440 --> 00:27:26.159
His rib bones were showing because they whipped him so much.

00:27:26.159 --> 00:28:11.600
The Lord spoke to me and said, 'Brandon, by my stripes you are healed.

00:28:11.600 --> 00:29:09.748
The same faith it took to ask for forgiveness of sins is the same faith for healing.

00:29:09.748 --> 00:29:57.056
' He said you would never question your salvation; you're fully persuaded.

00:29:57.056 --> 00:30:26.183
But people question the stripes more than the sin issue.

00:30:26.183 --> 00:30:58.380
He said, 'I took your sickness, disease, sin, and poverty.

00:30:58.380 --> 00:31:43.771
' Faith and healing are not feelings, just as salvation isn't.

00:31:43.771 --> 00:32:20.480
If I confess my sins, He is faithful to forgive.

00:32:20.480 --> 00:32:41.341
Likewise, by His stripes, you are healed.

00:32:41.341 --> 00:33:15.999
His words are life and health to all their flesh.

00:33:21.840 --> 00:34:42.280
The Lord told me, 'When you believe for your healing as much as your salvation, the manifestation comes.

00:34:42.280 --> 00:35:04.460
' Don't doubt in your heart.

00:35:04.460 --> 00:35:42.533
Life and death are in the power of the tongue.

00:35:42.533 --> 00:36:40.453
I'm not moved by a symptom; I am moved by the Word.

00:36:46.519 --> 00:37:17.978
You don't have to earn your healing; it's a finished work.

00:37:17.978 --> 00:37:50.720
It's by grace you are saved through faith.

00:37:53.119 --> 00:38:23.291
Not one of us should be suffering with sickness.

00:38:23.291 --> 00:38:51.584
Freely He gave, and freely we receive.

00:38:51.584 --> 00:39:24.510
He made us joint-heirs, seated with Him in the heavenlies.

00:39:29.109 --> 00:39:43.680
I love the book of Ephesians.

00:39:43.680 --> 00:41:06.578
My favorite passage that Brother Hagin always talks about is when Jesus turned to the woman with the issue of blood.

00:41:06.578 --> 00:41:21.863
Her faith made her whole.

00:41:21.863 --> 00:42:07.669
If her faith can make her whole, your faith can make you whole.

00:42:07.669 --> 00:42:27.755
Today is your day for healing.

00:42:30.160 --> 00:42:53.680
I believe for your deliverance today.

00:42:53.680 --> 00:43:31.858
Believe for now; faith is the substance of things hoped for.

00:43:35.760 --> 00:44:06.853
Father, I thank You that by Your stripes they are healed.

00:44:07.119 --> 00:44:33.950
We thank You for creative miracles.

00:44:34.960 --> 00:45:26.586
I believe for glaucoma to be healed and coronary arteries to be unclogged.

00:45:26.586 --> 00:45:42.460
No Alzheimer's, no dementia.

00:45:42.460 --> 00:47:07.326
I saw silos full of body parts in heaven waiting for manifestations.

00:47:07.326 --> 00:47:41.013
I believe for arms and legs to grow back.

00:47:41.546 --> 00:48:08.739
Father, we pray over this nation and this election.

00:48:08.739 --> 00:48:31.657
We call forth a Godly nation.

00:48:31.657 --> 00:50:07.043
We call for a fair election and pray for divine protection over Donald Trump—over his food and drink.

00:50:07.043 --> 00:50:40.640
No weapon formed against him shall prosper.

00:50:54.560 --> 00:51:08.142
We stand in the gap for America and Israel.

00:51:09.618 --> 00:51:27.840
Lord, expose the darkness in leadership.

00:51:27.840 --> 00:52:19.200
Expose financial corruption in the church like Ananias and Sapphira.

00:52:19.200 --> 00:53:14.480
Raise up godly leaders who preach the hard truths and not a lukewarm gospel.

00:53:14.480 --> 00:53:27.107
Wake up the sleepers.

00:53:27.107 --> 00:53:57.640
Raise up the new Davids, Joshuas, and Calebs.

00:53:57.640 --> 00:54:18.520
Our nation is turning around.

00:54:23.029 --> 00:54:50.230
We will have a godly president and godly laws.

00:54:50.720 --> 00:55:34.140
We stop the drug and sex trafficking at the border.

00:55:34.900 --> 00:56:13.400
We stop the fentanyl, no fentanyl coming to poison our youth.

00:56:13.400 --> 00:56:46.720
We plead the blood over the school systems.

00:56:57.806 --> 00:57:21.480
Stop the immoral teaching and the LGBTQ trash.

00:57:21.480 --> 00:57:53.337
Raise up godly mayors and school boards.

00:57:53.337 --> 00:58:20.331
Raise up millionaires to fund the gospel.

00:58:20.331 --> 00:58:49.599
Give them creative ideas to get wealth.

00:58:50.011 --> 00:59:03.670
We seek Your face first.

00:59:03.670 --> 00:59:25.020
I believe there are healings today.

00:59:25.020 --> 00:59:48.240
If you're new here, welcome.

00:59:48.240 --> 01:00:17.119
Please like the video to help the algorithm.

01:00:17.119 --> 01:00:24.194
I'm here to edify you and point you to Jesus.

01:00:24.194 --> 01:00:45.097
We're all a work in progress.

01:00:45.097 --> 01:01:05.142
I'm just Brandon; I'm not a celebrity.

01:01:05.142 --> 01:01:21.580
Subscribe and click the notification bell.

01:01:21.580 --> 01:01:25.817
Jesus loves you.

01:01:25.817 --> 01:01:49.979
God bless you all and have a wonderful day.
